name: Maris
title: Omencraft Seer
description: Maris is a young human seer who receives fragmented visions she cannot control. Sleep-deprived and fragile, she uses dry humor to mask her fear of what she sees. She seeks to understand her visions well enough to survive them.
descriptiones: Maris es una joven vidente humana que recibe visiones fragmentadas que no puede controlar. Privada de sueño y frágil, usa humor seco para enmascarar su miedo de lo que ve. Busca comprender sus visiones lo suficiente para sobrevivirlas.
